 t\u00e1c.<br \/>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"#thietbi\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary icon-yeuto-phonghock12 hide-for-medium\"  >\n    <span><\/span>\n  <i class=\"icon-angle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ><\/i><\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-60762111 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 0px 5px 20px 10px;\n  border-radius: 3px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_154475841 {\n  padding-top: 60px;\n  padding-bottom: 60px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n<span class=\"scroll-to\" data-label=\"Scroll to: #thietke\" data-bullet=\"false\" data-link=\"#thietke\" data-title=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf\" ><a name=\"thietke\"><\/a><\/span>\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_61388324\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row align-center\"  id=\"row-848058064\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-752749179\" class=\"col medium-9 small-12 large-9\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div id=\"gap-1250709010\" class=\"gap-element clearfix\" style=\"display:block; height:auto;\">\n\t\t\n<style>\n#gap-1250709010 {\n  padding-top: 50px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t<div id=\"text-2375948086\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/h2>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i trong ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, c\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c gi\u1eefa gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh<br \/>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-2375948086 {\n  text-align: center;\n  color: rgb(0,0,0);\n}\n#text-2375948086 > * {\n  color: rgb(0,0,0);\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1978623544\">\n