t\t\n<h4>Linh ho\u1ea1t<\/h4>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-1880328244 {\n  text-align: left;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_111803426 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n}\n#section_111803426 .section-bg-overlay {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.593);\n}\n#section_111803426 .section-bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: 14452;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n<span class=\"scroll-to\" data-label=\"Scroll to: #moitruong\" data-bullet=\"false\" data-link=\"#moitruong\" data-title=\"M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" ><a name=\"moitruong\"><\/a><\/span>\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_1108760455\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row align-center\"  id=\"row-370842239\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1273996878\" class=\"col medium-10 small-12 large-10\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div id=\"text-4207841990\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<h2>Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/h2>\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i kh\u1ed1i K12 nh\u1eb1m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc sinh v\u1ec1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<br \/>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-4207841990 {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"row row-thanthien-phonghock12\"  id=\"row-2054320598\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1150947502\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\" >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1251946122\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1607241850\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_766222150\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-animate=\"fadeInRight\">\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"922\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Chat-lieu-than-thien-922x800-1.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Chat-lieu-than-thien-922x800-1.webp 922w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Chat-lieu-than-thien-922x800-1-461x400.webp 461w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Chat-lieu-than-thien-922x800-1-768x666.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Chat-lieu-than-thien-922x800-1-600x521.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 922px) 100vw, 922px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_766222150 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-1607241850 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 50px 0px 0px 0px;\n  margin: 0px 0px -100px -2px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1442738953\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng laminate v\u00e0 melamine trong gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u t\u00e1i ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00ean m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><i class=\"fas fa-check\"><\/i> S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u Laminate c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, an to\u00e0n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t laminate c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt l\u00fd t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc,\u2026 Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m laminate c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n t\u1ed1t, tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb bay m\u00e0u gi\u1ea3m t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9<\/p>\n<p><i class=\"fas fa-check\"><\/i> Melamine l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i nh\u1ef1a t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ph\u1ee7 g\u1ed7, t\u1ee7 v\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. Melamine c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1ee5c n\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c bi\u1ebfn d\u1ea1ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng lau ch\u00f9i v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd ho\u1eb7c h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-1442738953 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 15px 10px 0px 0px;\n  margin: 30px 0px 0px 0px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-1150947502 > .col-inner {\n  border-radius: 10px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t<div id=\"gap-1901472018\" class=\"gap-element clearfix\" style=\"display:block; height:auto;\">\n\t\t\n<style>\n#gap-1901472018 {\n  padding-top: 13px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_1108760455 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n  background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240);\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n<span class=\"scroll-to\" data-label=\"Scroll to: #thietbi\" data-bullet=\"false\" data-link=\"#thietbi\" data-title=\"Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb\" ><a name=\"thietbi\"><\/a><\/span>\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_1453097628\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row align-center\"  id=\"row-400935127\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-75823552\" class=\"col medium-11 small-12 large-11\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div id=\"text-2995639210\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<h2>Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7<\/h2>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-2995639210 {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t<div id=\"text-2304091066\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0o quy tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn.Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng minh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong vi\u1ec7c truy c\u1eadp ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n m\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi cho s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a. D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh t\u1eebng c\u1ea5p l\u1edbp thu\u1ed9c kh\u1ed1i THPT, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0: M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu\/Tivi\/M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb\/M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, Loa di \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3ng, Camera.<\/p>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-2304091066 {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover img-border-inno x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_756798515\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner image-cover dark\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\">\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1376\" height=\"917\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Phong-hoc-tieu-hoc.webp\" class=\"attachment-original size-original\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Phong-hoc-tieu-hoc.webp 1376w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Phong-hoc-tieu-hoc-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Phong-hoc-tieu-hoc-1200x800.webp 1200w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Phong-hoc-tieu-hoc-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1376px) 100vw, 1376px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_756798515 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-75823552 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 30px 0px 0px 0px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-107782481\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1225628301\" class=\"col medium-3 small-6 large-3 has-hover\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background-color:rgb(233, 233, 233);\" >\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"is-border hover-fade-in\"\n\t\tstyle=\"border-color:rgb(189, 0, 0);border-radius:5px;border-width:0px 0px 2px 0px;\">\n\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-top text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 60px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h3>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 h\u1eefu \u00edch trong vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c gi\u1eefa gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc, cho ph\u00e9p gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu n\u1ed9i dung, ghi ch\u00fa v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. H\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-1225628301 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 5px 5px 15px 10px;\n  border-radius: 5px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1432130759\" class=\"col medium-3 small-6 large-3 has-hover\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\" style=\"background-color:rgb(233, 233, 233);\" >\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"is-border hover-fade-in\"\n\t\tstyle=\"border-color:rgb(189, 0, 0);border-radius:5px;border-width:0px 0px 2px 0px;\">\n\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-top text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 60px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h3>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Camera<\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao an ninh trong ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh. C\u00e1c camera \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch h\u00e0nh vi gi\u00fap nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n h\u1ecdc sinh, ghi l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh vi kh\u00f4ng an to\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#